==English==
===Etymology===
From the [[Persian]] words &#1662;&#1575;&#1610;&#1580;&#1575;&#1605;&#1607; ''p&aelig; jama'' meaning ''leg garment'' via [[Urdu]]/[[Hindi]] word ''pajama''.

===Noun===
'''pajamas''' ''plural''
#[[Clothes]] for wearing to bed and sleeping in, usually consisting of a loose-fitting shirt and pants.

